Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.59,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.31,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:22.80,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:27.53,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:34.47,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You were 10, I was 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in our backyard garden that we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was crying. You alone saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you, my sister, knew of my tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was 10, you were 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in May, and such a bright day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my very first visit to the Ichinomiya family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the moment came,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you came into view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the beauty my mother had often mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? This is my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're from the maid's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and sit down. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was invited to a friend's birthday party, but... guess what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They seated me all the way at the foot of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the seat they gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never been treated so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she had a bad seat... is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you'll not repeat any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to your father, your mother, your brother... No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, it's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama! So this is where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the driver but not you so I was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't concern yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel well, so I left. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a regal bearing that I will never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were only a girl of 11, who was crying so hard only a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet your face was now clear and composed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you couldn't allow the maid to see your tears of humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My young heart trembled to see such pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...it thrilled me with such joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day, you have filled my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day, I've had eyes for no one but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you had fallen in love... tragically in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...painfully in love, with Takehiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For one brief summer, for one scant week...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You alone could have experienced such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,25. The Scarlet Lipstick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I called over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't been at school, not since Miya-sama's birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, yesterday I went to your apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something you wanted? Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Your apartment door was open all day yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to shut the door when you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you are, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! At the Sorority House?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... don't go right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be expecting you at 8 o'clock in the Sorority's Kisaragi Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,8 o'clock? In the Kisaragi Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. That's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on home first. Then come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The main gate will be closed then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She would like to discuss some important Sorority business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are matters she can only discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Only with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Miya-sama said. That should suffice. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sew each stitch, one by one, from your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and give character to your needlepoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a stitch, and think about Mom. Orihara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really expecting beautiful needlepoint from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But shouldn't you at least be able to sew on a button for your future husband.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a husband who can sew his own buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and maybe some nice needlepoint on your child's lunch bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if the lunch is a frozen one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mmmm....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking depressed all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to go see "Believe in Love" this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Today's the last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell Tomoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the movie you wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it'll be after 8 by the time the movie is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? So what's happening at 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama wants to see me at 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama? What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can answer a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Misonoo-san's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me... about her and Henmi Takehiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What luck! To get this close to Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... the two of them first met when she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you. I wanted to invite you to tomorrow's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko taught at the cram school Nanako-san attended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she made him into her brother and pen-pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother and pen-pal... Totally girlish, that's just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? It's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business? Sure. That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,School ended at 4, and my appointment wasn't until 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stay all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I went to see "Believe in Love" with Mariko-san and Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to leave in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I could make it to my appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... the movie "Believe in Love" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a bit more "adult" than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dropping in unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But not one drop has parted these lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get like this sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have question... for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So many questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make coffee. Come on, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So many questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to... I mustn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't even ask you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it, for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the sake of her self-respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They protested my leaving,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they were absorbed in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kisaragi Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kisaragi Room is a private lounge for the head of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it at the north end on the 2nd floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in. Come sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer. Come sit down, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from me. Come, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Come closer. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child, I had a doll with lips much like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See... beautiful, isn't it... this would suit you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, close your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...be very still, close your lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In two years, maybe three,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll be surprised how beautiful a lady you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...then, many fine men will be attracted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop seeing Henmi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... he's only...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew everything from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so adorable, I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...even back on Orientation Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So... forget Henmi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That magnificent bearing and composure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...the exquisite dignity that made me tremble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...such perfect pride... where is it all now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it! You love Henmi Takehiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you admitted this girl, Misonoo Nanako, into the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted her to worship you so much that she would leave Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother... and Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why... I'm in the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... that's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now finally, all is clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your intentions and your motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a stop to this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have degraded yourself and I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You would do well not to speak such lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, you mustn't believe any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you aren't going, then I will leave myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one was it? Which ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one? Which ear was touched by Miya-sama's lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be true? What Saint-Juste said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is in love with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that's why she chose me for the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep me away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wasn't actually qualified for the Sorority after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I worship you, Fukiko-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seems I can only hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I've spoken words which can't be unspoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My love for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I nurtured it... so deep within myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It grew magically, becoming a living treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...my very own treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My secret, invisible treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster! Drive faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I must resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I must resign from the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me fill you in on how "Believe in Love" ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How it ended?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you left in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It got so intriguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, Elizabeth discovered that Tom had a lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that lover was her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She caught them meeting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She was helpless to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She faced the end of the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what happened next...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad. She began traveling alone, still carrying his unborn child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Elizabeth? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow or the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In a while, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady! We weren't told to expect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That treasure was mine alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They destroyed it! They... they trampled on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
